{"id": "art-20292", "label": "Art. 20292", "title": "Art. 20292: Cuprinsul mandatului", "slug": "art-20292", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_154127450\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_154127450\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2029<sup>2</sup>:\nCuprinsul mandatului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_498323780\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1079\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_498323780\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Mandatul poate cuprinde dorin&#355;ele exprimate de\nmandant cu privire la îngrijirea sa &#351;i condi&#355;iile de via&#355;&#259;\ndup&#259; survenirea incapacit&#259;&#355;ii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2123448040\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1078\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2123448040\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Mandatul cuprinde persoana desemnat&#259; de mandant\nc&#259;reia mandatarul trebuie s&#259; îi dea socoteal&#259;, precum &#351;i\nfrecven&#355;a îndeplinirii acestei obliga&#355;ii, care nu poate fi mai mare\nde 3 ani. Dac&#259; mandantul nu a desemnat o asemenea persoan&#259;, aceasta\neste desemnat&#259; de instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;, cu ocazia\nîncuviin&#355;&#259;rii mandatului.</span></p>"}